ご視聴いただきありがとうございます。

お休みの日、トーストと卵とコーヒーを並べたテーブルで、ゆったりした朝食の時間をイメージした楽曲を並べました。

リラックスしたい時や、爽やかな気分に浸りたい時、朝活のお供に、このLo-Fi音楽を聴いてください。

comments.text:
It's AI. Look at the knife on the right and how the outside of the plate melts into it. That's the most obvious way to tell. Human artists know how to draw things separately (so, they draw the plate then the knife). AI doesn't have that capability, so they try to do both at the same time and often get confused and think they're the same object. Try to trace the outline of the plate with your mouse if you struggle to see what I mean --- it doesn't line up where the knife is.
There are also some smaller things which give it an AI vibe, but they could just be stylistic choices, so I think that checking for "melting" is the best method to check.
